div.span: Dump of reversed data from the original RocketLeague Init.bnk file, generated by a modified version of Wwiser.
Wwiser tool is available at:https://github.com/bnnm/wwiser (huge thanks to bnnm)
This file is for reference only, data here was used to get hashes and rebuild the RocketLeague Wwise Project by hand.
Every Bus, AuxBus, Effect, StateGroup, SwitchGroup, State, RTPC, Curve, and their params and references were taken from here.
Fixed AkSwitchGraphPoint not being correctly dumped.
Fixed Wwiser dumping a f32 on NonRTPC.uGameParamID instead of tid in Wwise Meter effect.
Fixed Wwiser dumping a f32 on AkPropBundle pID=0x1E [HDRBusGameParam] and pID=0x46 [AttenuationID] instead of tid.
Customized Wwiser dump XSL to avoid losing my eyes + Added ToggleAll button. (Should've done it WAY before though D: )
Updated to include current RocketLeague names for AudioModding release @ October 6th 2023
